itunes:title: FEELIN' 2022! Welcome To The New Year!
title: FEELIN' 2022! Welcome To The New Year!
description:
Welcome to 2022! Jessi and Stew have been traveling like crazy and that mixed in with the holiday's made a podcast break necessary. But we are back and better than ever, baby! In this episode we talk about our favorite memories from 2021 and manifest our goals for the new year. Don't forget that new episodes come every Tuesday! Follow us on Instagram and tell us your New Years resolutions!
